<subSubSection id="5DCA0485FFE9FF97B1AD56F4FD29FE62" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="156F570EFFE9FF97B1AD56F4FD5EFF36" blockId="102.[151,1437,150,609]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFE9FF97B1AD56F4FEF5FF7F" bold="true" box="[199,345,150,176]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Distribution</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFE9FF97B00356F5FDE4FF7E" box="[361,584,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Pseudococcidae" genus="Phenacoccus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFE9FF97B00356F5FDE4FF7E" box="[361,584,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Phenacoccus solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known from 42 countries in the Afrotropical, Nearctic, Neotropical, Oriental and Palaearctic Regions (
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFE9FF97B08756D9FCB4FF19" author="Garcia Morales M. &amp; Denno, B. D. &amp; Miller, D. R. &amp; Miller, G. L. &amp; Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B." box="[493,792,187,214]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" refId="ref89637" refString="Garcia Morales M., Denno, B. D., Miller, D. R., Miller, G. L., Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B. (2016) ScaleNet: a literature-based model of scale insect biology and systematics. Database. Available from: http: // scalenet. info (accessed 30 January 2021) https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / database / bav 118" type="url" year="2016">
García Morales 
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFE9FF97B3CB56D9FD7DFF1A" box="[673,721,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
) including 
<collectingCountry id="6DC7179EFFE9FF97B2FC56D9FC6AFF1A" box="[918,966,187,213]" name="Iran" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Iran</collectingCountry>
, where it has been recorded from 
<collectingRegion id="D71499ECFFE9FF97B45156D9FA34FF1A" box="[1339,1432,187,213]" country="Iran" name="Esfahan" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Esfahan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="D71499ECFFE9FF97B1FD56BDFF66FF36" box="[151,202,223,249]" country="Iran" name="Fars" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Fars</collectingRegion>
, and 
<collectingRegion id="D71499ECFFE9FF97B06E56BDFEFDFF36" box="[260,337,223,249]" country="Iran" name="Tehran" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Tehran</collectingRegion>
provinces (
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFE9FF97B0BE56BDFD4AFF36" author="Moghaddam, M. &amp; Hatami, B. &amp; Zibaii, K. &amp; Sabzalian, M. R." box="[468,742,223,249]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" pagination="135 - 136" refId="ref95508" refString="Moghaddam, M., Hatami, B., Zibaii, K. &amp; Sabzalian, M. R. (2004) [Report of Phenacoccus solani (Hom.: Coccoidea: Pseudococcidae) from Iran]. Journal of Entomological Society of Iran, 24 (1), 135 - 136." type="journal article" year="2004">
Moghaddam 
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFE9FF97B30056BDFD0FFF36" box="[618,675,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">et al.</emphasis>
2004
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="156F570EFFE9FF97B1AD5761FB41FEA9" blockId="102.[151,1437,150,609]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFE9FF97B1AD5761FEFDFED2" bold="true" box="[199,337,259,285]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Host-plants</emphasis>
: The species has been recorded on host-plants in 89 genera belonging to 35 families (
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFE9FF97B4725761FEE7FE8D" author="Garcia Morales M. &amp; Denno, B. D. &amp; Miller, D. R. &amp; Miller, G. L. &amp; Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B." pageId="102" pageNumber="103" refId="ref89637" refString="Garcia Morales M., Denno, B. D., Miller, D. R., Miller, G. L., Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B. (2016) ScaleNet: a literature-based model of scale insect biology and systematics. Database. Available from: http: // scalenet. info (accessed 30 January 2021) https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / database / bav 118" type="url" year="2016">
García Morales 
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFE9FF97B1B85745FEAEFE8E" box="[210,258,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry id="6DC7179EFFE9FF97B0135745FE05FE8E" box="[377,425,295,321]" name="Iran" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Iran</collectingCountry>
, it has been recorded on 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFE9FF97B3DF5745FCC4FE8E" box="[693,872,295,321]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Amaranthaceae</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFE9FF97B21B5745FB8EFE8F" box="[881,1058,295,321]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Celosia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cristata">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFE9FF97B21B5745FB8EFE8F" box="[881,1058,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Celosia cristata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
